OL,3,CBishop of Rochester says Church
OL,4,Csafeguarding needs 'change in culture'
OL,6,FRt Rev Jonathan Gibbs, The Bishop of
OL,7,FRochester said: "This decision
OL,8,Freflects the Synod's grave concerns
OL,9,Fregarding the findings of multiple
OL,10,Findependent reports highlighting
OL,11,Fsafeguarding failures and systemic
OL,12,Fissues within the Church of England.
OL,14,F"This motion is not a call for
OL,15,Fcondemnation but a humble
OL,16,Facknowledgment of the Church's shared
OL,17,Fresponsibility to protect the
OL,18,Fvulnerable and rebuild trust.
