OL,3,CBishop of Rochester says Church
OL,4,Csafeguarding needs 'change in culture'
OL,6,F"We call upon the Archbishops' Council
OL,7,Fto undertake urgent and meaningful
OL,8,Freforms, as recommended by the
OL,9,Freports, to ensure accountability,
OL,10,Fprofessionalism, and transparency in
OL,11,Fsafeguarding.
OL,13,F"As members of the body of Christ, we
OL,14,Fremain committed to advocating for a
OL,15,FChurch that is safe, inclusive, and
OL,16,Fresponsive to those it serves."
